<inglise> (c) provide, in the case of land transferred with a view to improving the environment, for the allocation of the reference quantity available on the holding concerned to the departing producer if he intends continuing milk production, </inglise>
<eesti> c) n&auml;ha ette asjassepuutuva talumajapidamise kvoodi andmine maa kasutamisest loobunud tootjale, kes kavatseb piimatootmist j&auml;tkata, juhul kui loobumine toimus keskkonna parandamist silmas pidades, </eesti>
<inglise> (d) determine, on the basis of objective criteria, the regions or collection areas within which the definitive transfer of reference quantities without transfer of the corresponding land is authorised, with the aim of improving the structure of milk production, </inglise>
<eesti> d) m&auml;&auml;rata objektiivsete tunnuste alusel kindlaks piirkonnad v&otilde;i varumisalad, mille puhul piimatootmise struktuuri parandamiseks lubatakse kvootide &uuml;lekandmist, ilma et l&auml;heks &uuml;le vastav maavaldus, </eesti>
<inglise> (e) authorise, upon application by the producer to the competent authority or the body designated by that authority, the definitive transfer of reference quantities without transfer of the corresonding land, or vice versa, with the aim of improving the structure of milk production at the level of the holding or to allow for extensification of production. </inglise>
<eesti> e) kui tootja esitab taotluse p&auml;devale asutusele v&otilde;i selle asutuse m&auml;&auml;ratud organile, v&otilde;ib selleks, et parandada piimatootmise struktuuri talumajapidamise tasandil v&otilde;i v&otilde;imaldada tootmise ekstensiivistamist, lubada kvootide l&otilde;plikku &uuml;lekandmist ilma vastava maavalduse &uuml;leminekuta v&otilde;i vastupidi. </eesti>
<inglise> The rules under (a), (b), (c) and (e) may be implemented at national level or at the appropriate territorial level or in collection areas." </inglise>
<eesti> Punktides a, b, c ja e esitatud eeskirju v&otilde;ib rakendada riigi tasandil v&otilde;i asjakohasel territoriaalsel tasandil v&otilde;i varumisaladel." </eesti>
